OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781581669
OL,3,CPalestine Action terror ban upheld by
OL,4,CCourt of Appeal
OL,6,FThe decision to ban Palestine Action
OL,7,Fas a terror group was lawful, the
OL,8,FCourt of Appeal ruled on Monday.
OL,10,FThis overturns a ruling by three
OL,11,Fjudges at the High Court in February,
OL,12,Fwhich found that the then-home
OL,13,Fsecretary Yvette Cooper's decision to
OL,14,Fproscribe Palestine Action under the
OL,15,FTerrorism Act 2000 last year was
OL,16,Funlawful, following a legal challenge
OL,17,Ffrom the group's co-founder, Huda
OL,18,FAmmori.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781581669
OL,3,CPalestine Action terror ban upheld by
OL,4,CCourt of Appeal
OL,6,FThe ban, which began on July 5 last
OL,7,Fyear, made membership of, or support
OL,8,Ffor, the direct action group a
OL,9,Fcriminal offence punishable by up to
OL,10,F14 years in prison, and has remained
OL,11,Fin force as the Home Office attempted
OL,12,Fto challenge the ruling.
OL,14,FAt the Court of Appeal on Monday, five
OL,15,Fjudges said the ban was a "justified
OL,16,Fand proportionate" interference on
OL,17,Ffreedom of expression rights.
OL,26,@wD@[OUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
