CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781581669
OL,3,CPalestine Action terror ban upheld by
OL,4,CCourt of Appeal
OL,6,FIn a summary of the decision, the Lady
OL,7,FChief Justice Baroness Carr said the
OL,8,FHigh Court had "materially understated
OL,9,Fthe position" when considering how
OL,10,Fmuch latitude the Home Secretary had
OL,11,Fwhen deciding whether to proscribe.
OL,13,FThe judge later said that comparisons
OL,14,Fto groups such as the suffragettes
OL,15,Fwere "seriously flawed".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781581669
OL,3,CPalestine Action terror ban upheld by
OL,4,CCourt of Appeal
OL,6,FBaroness Carr, sitting with Sir
OL,7,FGeoffrey Vos, Lord Justice Edis, Lord
OL,8,FJustice Lewis and Lady Justice
OL,9,FWhipple, continued: "There is a
OL,10,Fdistinction between the expression of
OL,11,Fan opinion or belief that is
OL,12,Fsupportive of the objective of an
OL,13,Forganisation... and an expression of
OL,14,Fan opinion or belief that is
OL,15,Fsupportive of an organisation itself."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
