OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781581669
OL,3,CPalestine Action terror ban upheld by
OL,4,CCourt of Appeal
OL,6,FIn the appeal, Sir James Eadie KC said
OL,7,Fin written submissions for the Home
OL,8,FOffice that "the line between
OL,9,Fcriminality, sometimes violent
OL,10,Fcriminality, and terrorism is not a
OL,11,Fbright one", and that the criminal law
OL,12,Fhad "demonstrably failed" to prevent
OL,13,Fthe escalation of the group's
OL,14,Factivities.
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
