CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781581669
OL,3,CPalestine Action terror ban upheld by
OL,4,CCourt of Appeal
OL,6,FBut Raza Husain KC, for Ms Ammori,
OL,7,Fsaid in written submissions that the
OL,8,FHigh Court was right to find that the
OL,9,Fban on the group did not correctly
OL,10,Fbalance the human rights involved and
OL,11,Fthat the ban on Palestine Action has
OL,12,Fcreated a "culture of fear" among
OL,13,Fcampaigners for Palestinian rights.
OL,15,FHundreds of people have been arrested
OL,16,Facross multiple demonstrations after
OL,17,Fholding up placards and wearing badges
OL,18,Fand t-shirts declaring support for
OL,19,FPalestine Action.
