OL,3,CPalestine Action terror ban upheld by
OL,4,CCourt of Appeal
OL,6,FThe Chief Magistrate has put a pause
OL,7,Fon the progress of criminal cases for
OL,8,Fthose charged, with a review hearing
OL,9,Fdue to take place on June 30.
OL,11,FThe Court of Appeal's decision comes
OL,12,Fafter four Palestine Action activists
OL,13,Fwho mounted a "terrorist" raid on
OL,14,FIsrael-based defence firm Elbit
OL,15,FSystems' UK factory were jailed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
