PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781581669
OL,3,CPalestine Action terror ban upheld by
OL,4,CCourt of Appeal
OL,6,FCharlotte Head, 30, Samuel Corner, 23,
OL,7,FLeona Kamio, 30, and Fatema Rajwani,
OL,8,F21, used sledgehammers and crowbars to
OL,9,Fdestroy computers, drones and other
OL,10,Fequipment before police and security
OL,11,Fintervened.
OL,13,FCorner, a former student at Oxford,
OL,14,Fstruck police officer Kate Evans twice
OL,15,Fon the back with a seven-pound
OL,16,Fsledgehammer, leaving her with a
OL,17,Ffractured spine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
