PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781581669
OL,3,CPalestine Action terror ban upheld by
OL,4,CCourt of Appeal
OL,6,FMr Justice Johnson gave the four
OL,7,Fprison sentences of between seven
OL,8,Fyears and eight months and four years
OL,9,Fand eight months, with each defendant
OL,10,Falso spending an extra year on licence.
OL,12,FDuring the hearing on Friday, the
OL,13,Fjudge ruled that the raid amounted to
OL,14,Fan "act of terrorism", having been
OL,15,Fcarried out to try to influence the UK
OL,16,FGovernment and intimidate a section of
OL,17,Fthe public.
